{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "mmf-api-collection-2026",
    "name": "Midwest Military — Full API",
    "description": "All WordPress + Next.js API endpoints for Midwest Military Fasteners.\n\n## Sidebar category logic — start here\n1. **WP Spec Parts — Categories Tree** — parent (Screws/Nuts/Washers) → children → `series[]`\n2. **WP Spec Parts — Category by Slug** — single sub-category with its series\n3. **WP Spec Parts — Products (by category)** — products in a sub-category\n4. **WP Spec Parts — Products (by category + series)** — filtered listing\n5. **Next.js — Catalog Categories** — same tree via frontend proxy\n\n## Variables\n- `next_base_url` → http://localhost:3000\n- `wp_base_url` → your WordPress site URL\n- `category_slug` → e.g. flat-washers, misc\n- `series_slug` → e.g. ms35308\n\n## Auth\nLogin via **Next.js — Auth Login** or **WP — Auth Login**, then cookies are set automatically for cart routes.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "next_base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "wp_base_url",
      "value": "https://dev-mmf-wp.pantheonsite.io",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "wp_api",
      "value": "{{wp_base_url}}/wp-json",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "category_slug",
      "value": "flat-washers",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "series_slug",
      "value": "ms35308",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "product_sku",
      "value": "MS35308-4",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "product_id",
      "value": "4129",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "cart_item_key",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "category_term_id",
      "value": "42",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "wc_nonce",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "wc_cart_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01 — Sidebar & Catalog (START HERE)",
      "description": "Endpoints used to build the product sidebar: Screws / Nuts / Washers → sub-categories → product series.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "WP — Categories Tree (sidebar source)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{wp_api}}/spec-parts/v1/categories",
            "description": "Returns normalized tree:\n```\n[\n  {\n    \"slug\": \"washers\",\n    \"children\": [\n      {\n        \"slug\": \"flat-washers\",\n        \"series\": [\n          { \"id\": 1, \"name\": \"MS35308\", \"slug\": \"ms35308\", \"count\": 5 }\n        ]\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n]\n```\nCheck `children[].series` for each sub-category."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "WP — Category by Slug",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{wp_api}}/spec-parts/v1/categories/slug/{{category_slug}}",
            "description": "Single category term with `series[]` — used for category hero + breadcrumb."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "WP — All Series Terms",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{wp_api}}/spec-parts/v1/series",
            "description": "All product-series taxonomy terms."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "WP — Products by Category",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{wp_api}}/spec-parts/v1/products?category={{category_slug}}&per_page=10&page=1",
              "host": [
                "{{wp_api}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "spec-parts",
                "v1",
                "products"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "category",
                  "value": "{{category_slug}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "per_page",
                  "value": "10"
                },
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Products in a sub-category. Each product has `product_series[]`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "WP — Products by Category + Series",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{wp_api}}/spec-parts/v1/products?category={{category_slug}}&series={{series_slug}}&per_page=10&page=1",
              "host": [
                "{{wp_api}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "spec-parts",
                "v1",
                "products"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "category",
                  "value": "{{category_slug}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "series",
                  "value": "{{series_slug}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "per_page",
                  "value": "10"
                },
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Filtered product listing when user clicks a series link in sidebar."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "WP — Product Series Taxonomy (wp/v2)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{wp_api}}/wp/v2/product-series?per_page=100&orderby=name&order=asc",
              "host": [
                "{{wp_api}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "wp",
                "v2",
                "product-series"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "per_page",
                  "value": "100"
                },
                {
                  "key": "orderby",
                  "value": "name"
                },
                {
                  "key": "order",
                  "value": "asc"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Fallback series list used by frontend sidebar builder."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "WP — Products in Category (series field)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{wp_api}}/wp/v2/product?product_cat={{category_term_id}}&per_page=100&_fields=id,product-series&orderby=id&order=asc",
              "host": [
                "{{wp_api}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "wp",
                "v2",
                "product"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "product_cat",
                  "value": "{{category_term_id}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "per_page",
                  "value": "100"
                },
                {
                  "key": "_fields",
                  "value": "id,product-series"
                },
                {
                  "key": "orderby",
                  "value": "id"
                },
                {
                  "key": "order",
                  "value": "asc"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Used by frontend to infer which series belong to a category when `series[]` is empty in categories API. Set `category_term_id` from categories tree response."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Next.js — Catalog Categories Proxy",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{next_base_url}}/api/catalog/categories",
            "description": "Next.js proxy — same data as WP categories tree, used by sidebar cache."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Next.js — Catalog Products Proxy",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{next_base_url}}/api/catalog/products?category={{category_slug}}&series={{series_slug}}&per_page=10&page=1",
              "host": [
                "{{next_base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "catalog",
                "products"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "category",
                  "value": "{{category_slug}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "series",
                  "value": "{{series_slug}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "per_page",
                  "value": "10"
                },
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
