    {
      "name": "07 — Checkout & Tax (WC Store API)",
      "description": "TAX TEST FLOW — run top to bottom:\n\n1. **Store Cart (get session)** — captures Nonce + Cart-Token into variables automatically\n2. **Add Item** — puts a product in the cart\n3. **Update Customer (MI address)** — THE TAX TEST: response `totals.total_tax` must be > 0 (e.g. \"863\" = $8.63 for 6% MI). Amounts are in minor units (cents).\n4. **Cart Totals (verify)** — re-check totals any time\n5. **Checkout Locations** — country/state dropdown data (requires latest api.php deployed)\n\nTax comes from TaxJar via WooCommerce — it is calculated only AFTER a customer address with a correct 2-letter state code (MI, not Michigan) is set.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1 — Store Cart (get session: nonce + cart token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const nonce = pm.response.headers.get('Nonce');",
                  "const token = pm.response.headers.get('Cart-Token');",
                  "if (nonce) pm.collectionVariables.set('wc_nonce', nonce);",
                  "if (token) pm.collectionVariables.set('wc_cart_token', token);",
                  "console.log('nonce:', nonce, '| cart-token saved:', Boolean(token));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{wp_base_url}}/wp-json/wc/store/v1/cart",
            "description": "First call — captures `Nonce` and `Cart-Token` response headers into collection variables (see Tests tab). All later Store API calls send them back."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2 — Add Item to Cart",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const nonce = pm.response.headers.get('Nonce');",
                  "const token = pm.response.headers.get('Cart-Token');",
                  "if (nonce) pm.collectionVariables.set('wc_nonce', nonce);",
                  "if (token) pm.collectionVariables.set('wc_cart_token', token);",
                  "console.log('nonce:', nonce, '| cart-token saved:', Boolean(token));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Nonce",
                "value": "{{wc_nonce}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Cart-Token",
                "value": "{{wc_cart_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": {{product_id}},\n  \"quantity\": 1\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{wp_base_url}}/wp-json/wc/store/v1/cart/add-item",
            "description": "Set `product_id` variable first (use WP — Product by SKU to resolve). 201 = added."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3 — Update Customer (MI address) ⇒ TAX TEST",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const d = pm.response.json();",
                  "const tax = d.totals && d.totals.total_tax;",
                  "pm.test('total_tax is present', () => pm.expect(tax).to.exist);",
                  "pm.test('total_tax > 0 (TaxJar applied)', () => pm.expect(Number(tax)).to.be.above(0));",
                  "console.log('TAX =', tax, 'minor units → $' + (Number(tax)/100).toFixed(2));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Nonce",
                "value": "{{wc_nonce}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Cart-Token",
                "value": "{{wc_cart_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"shipping_address\": {\n    \"first_name\": \"Test\",\n    \"last_name\": \"User\",\n    \"address_1\": \"100 Main St\",\n    \"city\": \"Detroit\",\n    \"state\": \"MI\",\n    \"postcode\": \"48226\",\n    \"country\": \"US\"\n  },\n  \"billing_address\": {\n    \"first_name\": \"Test\",\n    \"last_name\": \"User\",\n    \"address_1\": \"100 Main St\",\n    \"city\": \"Detroit\",\n    \"state\": \"MI\",\n    \"postcode\": \"48226\",\n    \"country\": \"US\",\n    \"email\": \"test@example.com\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{wp_base_url}}/wp-json/wc/store/v1/cart/update-customer",
            "description": "THE TAX TEST. Response `totals.total_tax` should be > 0 (\"863\" = $8.63 at 6% MI on $143.75). State MUST be the 2-letter code. Tests tab asserts it automatically — green = tax working."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4 — Cart Totals (verify)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const nonce = pm.response.headers.get('Nonce');",
                  "const token = pm.response.headers.get('Cart-Token');",
                  "if (nonce) pm.collectionVariables.set('wc_nonce', nonce);",
                  "if (token) pm.collectionVariables.set('wc_cart_token', token);",
                  "console.log('nonce:', nonce, '| cart-token saved:', Boolean(token));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Nonce",
                "value": "{{wc_nonce}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Cart-Token",
                "value": "{{wc_cart_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{wp_base_url}}/wp-json/wc/store/v1/cart",
            "description": "Full cart with `totals.total_tax`, `totals.total_price`, `shipping_rates[]`."
          }
        },
